    "The authors observed that South China Morning Post and The Standard, which are two popular English newspapers in Hong Kong, were not included in the \"Hong Kong Media\", therefore, these newspapers were searched separately within its official website, and 5 additional articles were added.",
    "In total, 31 news articles were selected.To ensure more details of an event can be captured, the authors group together duplicate articles of the same event that are published in different newspapers during analysis.",
    "A timeline (Table 1) was created to track the development in the last eight months, to ensure this article is reader-friendly, the authors purposely cite the English news under the reference column, unless English news did not cover that event.",
    "The bracket shows the number of news coverage that has reported the same news.",
    "ResultsTo answer the second research question, the following section tries to break down the whole period into three phases and identified the challenges in making university policy and management adapt to the emergence of ChatGPT and other generative AI technologies in each stage."
